        [
          "From the first moment you swam with the whales you knew you wanted to do it for the rest of your life. First you went to college to study them, but the pull of the water was to powerful. You got a job at sea world and was soon one of their best anial handlers. Little did you know that vampries came to the park to have a uniqne feeding experince. You were embraced and have kept a low profile, at sea world for the last 10 years.. Until recently with the camrilla's push to in to mexico you were found. A rush acknowlagment, you tried to fit in there but you had trouble making friends. Hearing there was a norse gangrel in LA you decided to come up to hear his experinces of when the water just was teaming with life."
